title: [Vornavis, Outlands Road]
description: A brush-filled ravine drops toward the starlit waters of the Rockspawn River to the northeast, where the tops of willows peak above the steppe grasses.  To the southeast, hooves, boots and cart wheels have beaten a clear trail across the grassland.
